creator: Rise Buildings, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Rise Buildings is a property experience platform that manages all of the daily activities in a building for both staff and residents. With the Rise Living app, residents and property staff can manage the following tasks in the palm of their hand:

• Visitor Management
• Package Delivery
• Service Requests/Work Order Management
• Amenity Reservations
• Curated Vendors and Exclusive Deals
• Valet & Taxi Requests
• Payments
• Community Newsfeed, Groups, Events, Polls, & Building Updates
• Marketplace
• Direct & Group Messaging
• Document Vault
• And much more!

The Rise Living app allows you to streamline these everyday tasks and elevate your property.

title: Rise Living

creator: Rise Buildings, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Rise Buildings is a property operations and experience platform that manages everything that takes place within your building. With the Rise Living app, tenants and property staff can interact with their building all from the palm of their hand.

Download the app to:
•Register visitors
•Interact with management and fellow tenants via the news feed, message groups, events, and polls
•Submit and manage service requests
•Reserve amenity spaces
•Receive notifications for package arrival
•See curated vendors and exclusive deals
•Request your vehicle from valet
•Use your phone as a digital key to access the building
•Book fitness classes
•See what’s for sale in the peer-to-peer marketplace
•And much more!
*Note: features vary by property

Contact us at support@risebuildings.com with any questions about the platform.

Rise Buildings is a property operations and experience platform that manages everything that takes place within your building. With the Rise Living app, tenants and property staff can interact with their building all from the palm of their hand.

Download the app to:
•Register visitors
•Interact with management and fellow tenants via the news feed, message groups, events, and polls
•Submit and manage service requests
•Reserve amenity spaces
•Receive notifications for package arrival
•See curated vendors and exclusive deals
•Request your vehicle from valet
•Use your phone as a digital key to access the building
•Book fitness classes
•See what’s for sale in the peer-to-peer marketplace
•And much more!
*Note: features vary by property

Contact us at support@risebuildings.com with any questions about the platform.
